\textbf{Step 1. Base rank \texttt{rank(i)}}
\[
\tilde r_i \;=\; \frac{\sinh\!\left(\left(\frac{n+1}{2}-i\right)\lambda\right)}{\sinh\!\left(\frac{n+1}{2}\lambda\right) - \sinh\!\left(\frac{n-1}{2}\lambda\right)}
